Santee.Santana High School:
Santana High School, located in Santee, California, is part of the Grossmont Union High School District.


== 2001 shooting ==
On March 5, 2001, fifteen-year-old Charles Andrew Williams killed two, and wounded thirteen at Santana High School. Bryan Zuckor, a fellow student, was the first killed, as he and another student, Trevor Edwards, were shot in the bathroom where Williams began.
